<div id='lengthSection'>

	<p>
		Now we need to know the length of railing you will need.
		We will need you to provide us with an estimate of the length needed, in feet. When you figured out the proper
		length of railing needed, please round that figure if it is a decimal. Keep in mind that while we want you
		to be as accurate as possible with your estimate, we will confirm your measurements ourselves after you place
		your order.
	</p>

