			measure the edges of the deck that will need railings. Any part of the deck that is lined up against a wall or
			an opening should not be measured.
			If you need more help, please click <a href='faqs#deckMeasuringHelp' class='spaceBefore' target='_blank'>here</a>.
		</p>
    </div>

